{"tid":420620,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"救而家條女定換新女好?","createTime":"2017-10-01T14:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T16:06:09.000Z","uid":52636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"492f8256037891c05baa147400d34ff0952908d0","tid":420620,"uid":52636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"HKNOTEBOOK 2011果時識左條女, 叫 FUJITSU SH561<br />\n<br />\nFUJITSU LifeBook SH561<br />\n‧WIN 10 專業版<br />\n‧Intel Core i5-2410M <br />\n‧Intel HM65 <br />\n‧NVIDIA GeForce GT520M<br />\n‧8 GB DDR3 1333<br />\n‧640 GB HDD<br />\n<br />\n因為上次拎出街果時跌爆左個MON, 而家長期插住個外置MON吊住條命<br />\n多數上下網煲下劇, 得閒玩兩鋪LOL (全部SET最低)<br />\n<br />\n但係呢排用用下越來越慢, 本身都有諗過換過部desktop, 但係見而家煙條D牙膏仲擠緊, 粒I5好似仲用得下, 咁我應唔應該救而家條女? (考慮到BUDGET同用途方面, 好似唔係咁大需要全部換曬)<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下有無方法完全CUT走左NOTEBOOK個MON, 等佢DETECT唔到爆左果個MON? 我驚CLONE 左D野落SSD, 開機果時有野要SET但係個MON無得顯示出來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db262011895961431be61335cfe0920742aa846c","tid":420620,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"有錢咪換，冇錢咪唔換，最近出左第8代U，性能既飛躍係比以前抵買好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd7e6f905dabbacc2d0a8398bac09aeeadac727","tid":420620,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"Desktop Ryzen不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448fb9a67659718a301d9d781d8790fbbc196f33","tid":420620,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"轉Desktop要睇你有冇需要，見你拎得出街應該點都有少少，係香港換個mon都唔平，不如成部換，你依部應該都4 5年掛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671cb5935bf66bda45a26d6a312b4d4806334cc5","tid":420620,"uid":52636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci